---
title: Porktacular Bacon Fondue Brunch Platter with Maple Sausage, Roasted Potatoes & Garlic Toasts
description: What better way to toast to brunch with friends than diving and dipping into a shareable fondue? Topped with crispy, smoky bacon bits and served alongside roasted potatoes smothered in herby butter, hearty maple breakfast sausage, snappy green apples and garlicky toasted baguette rounds, this board has a little bit of everything you want to see in a great brunch spread. So go ahead: pick, graze, and dunk your way through ooey-gooey, cheesy deliciousness during the best meal of the week.
